          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Shark Sales Elimination Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill makes it illegal to possess, buy, or sell shark parts or any product containing shark parts.A person may possess a shark part that was lawfully taken consistent with a license or permit under certain circumstances.</p> <p> A violation of this bill's prohibition shall be treated as an act prohibited under the Magnuson-Stevens Fishery Conservation and Management Act.</p>]]></text>
          <actionDate>2017-05-16</actionDate>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        </item>
